| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 1 | Non-`readonly` struct causes 48-byte defensive copies |
| 🟡 Moderate | 3 | Oversized struct, ToString allocations, culture-aware compare |
| ℹ️ Info | 0 | — |

